#: ../../modules/backends/backends_cuda.rst:36
msgid ""
":class:`~qilisdk.backends.cuda_backend.CudaSamplingMethod.STATE_VECTOR`: "
"Full state-vector simulation (switches to CPU if a GPU is unavailable)."
